  "h = 5 min, 4 subintervals. Trapezoidal rule: (5/2)[10 + 2(14) + 2(18) + 2(16) + 12] = (5/2)(10 + 28 + 36 + 32 + 12) = (5/2)(118) = 295 liters.": ""
